title: MONDAY - Week 10 recap 2020
itunes:title: MONDAY - Week 10 recap 2020
description:
It was a battle of two former MVP's (0:06) as Cam Newton and the Patriots came out on top over Lamar Jackson and the Ravens. Hear what Newton had to say about Head Coach Bill Belichick and his "yoda-like" ways (0:39). In what could be the front-runner for play of the year (1:25) DeAndre Hopkins with the incredible game-winning catch as the Cardinals beat the Bills. Kyler Murray describes the play from his point of view (1:57). Plus, we have an update on Drew Brees and his injured ribs (3:12)
